data.description: Priced below accessed value and ready for you to call it home! West Lee County gated living!!!  Unit 212 Saxton Place --This fabulous home offers 2,068  sq ft of living space, 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths -- Recently painted -- The great room has built-in's, a fireplace and gorgeous wood floors -- Dining room with easy access to the kitchen and open to the family room --The kitchen has pretty wooden cabinets, granite counter-tops and all appliances stay! Spacious master suite has built-ins in the bedroom -- bathroom features a large vanity, a separate shower,  jetted tub and massive walk-in closet -- Both additional bedrooms are spacious with ample closet space -- Two storage closets in the hallway -- Huge laundry room with built-in cabinets, a laundry sink and great storage closet --  Nice size sun-room leading to the covered back porch  --The covered back porch provides a GORGEOUS VIEW of the lake!!! Plantation blinds -- Foam insulation in attic  Wired & speakers in place for surround sound  water softener   2 car garage and a low maintenance all brick exterior! -- The neighborhood offers gated access, walking trails, common area space, a gated entrance and TWO stocked lakes --  Association fees are $245/ month and cover lawn maintenance, the water for lawn irrigation, straw, common areas, trash pickup, termite bond and gate maintenance -- Quality Construction -- Convenient to everything
